{
  "id": "6a2f68b7a4ee1dacff9d959d",
  "title": "nyarlaさんのキー配列",
  "created": 1781491900,
  "updated": 1783346469,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2f68b7a4ee1dacff9d959d",
      "text": "nyarlaさんのキー配列",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491900,
      "updated": 1781491900
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f68bb0000000000882ecf",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491900,
      "updated": 1781491901
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f68bd0000000000882ed1",
      "text": "\t興味を持たれた方もいるみたいなので掲載してみます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491902,
      "updated": 1781493065
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6d4e0000000000882f03",
      "text": "\tこれは 2026年6月15日現在のモノです",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493070,
      "updated": 1781493085
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6d5d0000000000882f04",
      "text": "\t時期によっては細かい部分が変化する可能性もあります",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493085,
      "updated": 1781493102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f68bc0000000000882ed0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491901,
      "updated": 1781491901
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f68e60000000000882ed4",
      "text": "キーキャップの配列",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491942,
      "updated": 1781491967
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f68ff0000000000882ed6",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/9303eb612012af64d003884c35bebbb6]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491967,
      "updated": 1781491972
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f69070000000000882ed8",
      "text": "\tざっくり解説すると",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491975,
      "updated": 1781491999
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f691a0000000000882ed9",
      "text": "\t\t緑とオレンジはレイヤーキー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781491995,
      "updated": 1781492001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f69710000000000882ede",
      "text": "\t\t\t中央によってる Modifier のうち、上から二段目の特に印字がないキーキャップのことです",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492081,
      "updated": 1781492120
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f69280000000000882eda",
      "text": "\t\t`Ctrl` は Tap で `Enter` 、Hold で `Ctrl` として機能する",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492008,
      "updated": 1781492058
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f69430000000000882edb",
      "text": "\t\t`Shift` は Tap で `Space` 、Hold で `Shift` として動作する",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492035,
      "updated": 1781492069
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6d9d0000000000882f06",
      "text": "\tちなみに上記の写真は昔に撮ったもので、今の状態だと `S` の印字が磨り減っていたります",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493149,
      "updated": 1781493175
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6db70000000000882f07",
      "text": "\t\tあと最近掃除してないので結構汚れたりする",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493175,
      "updated": 1781493474
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6e7c0000000000882f0a",
      "text": "\tなお入力メソッドには SKK を利用しています",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493373,
      "updated": 1781493384
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6e880000000000882f0c",
      "text": "\t\tLinux だと `fcitx5-cskk` 、Windows だと `corvusskk` を使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493385,
      "updated": 1781493407
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6e9f0000000000882f0d",
      "text": "\t\tまたアルバイトで macOS を使ってた時は `AquaSKK` を使ってました",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781493407,
      "updated": 1781493424
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f699f0000000000882ee0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492127,
      "updated": 1781492127
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ac80000000000882ee1",
      "text": "[Vial] によるキーマップはこんな感じです[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492424,
      "updated": 1781492775
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6c710000000000882ef6",
      "text": "ただ今となっては使ってないキーもあるので、「これ何で入れてたんだっけ？」というのも入ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492849,
      "updated": 1781492878
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ad40000000000882ee3",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/6e1dc2882521d6bbe5996c78ea980b65]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492437,
      "updated": 1781492439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b340000000000882ee9",
      "text": "\t\t0番レイヤー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492532,
      "updated": 1781492542
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b3e0000000000882eeb",
      "text": "\t\tここはいつもの基点",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492542,
      "updated": 1781492548
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b440000000000882eec",
      "text": "\t\t`MO(1)` で 1番レイヤーへ `MO(2)` で2番レイヤーへ遷移する",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492548,
      "updated": 1781492590
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b740000000000882eed",
      "text": "\t\t昨日事故を起してしまったレイヤーはここが起因です",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492596,
      "updated": 1781492618
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b350000000000882eea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492534,
      "updated": 1781492534
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ad80000000000882ee5",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/4dc82f00f17f28757dd2d521e3822a24]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492440,
      "updated": 1781492454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b8d0000000000882eee",
      "text": " \t1番レイヤー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492622,
      "updated": 1781492800
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b960000000000882ef0",
      "text": " \t主に矢印キーと右上の記号類を入力するのに利用",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492630,
      "updated": 1781492800
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6bbd0000000000882ef1",
      "text": " \t`I`, `O`, `P` は左の Modifier と組み合わせてグローバルショーカットを入力するために使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492670,
      "updated": 1781492800
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b8e0000000000882eef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492622,
      "updated": 1781492622
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ac90000000000882ee2",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/453228cb352a9a7d7d31374b3304ebf3]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492426,
      "updated": 1781492468
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6bed0000000000882ef2",
      "text": "\t2番レイヤー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492718,
      "updated": 1781492735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6c020000000000882ef4",
      "text": "\t用途は主に左側の記号の入力と `MO`, `M1`, `M2` のマクロ入力",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492738,
      "updated": 1781492830
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6c5d0000000000882ef5",
      "text": "\t\tマクロについては固定文字列を入力するのに使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492830,
      "updated": 1781492840
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6bed0000000000882ef3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492718,
      "updated": 1781492718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ca10000000000882ef9",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/b9307e27dfbff135871c7cb899ac4e86]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492897,
      "updated": 1781492898
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ca30000000000882efb",
      "text": "\t\t3番レイヤー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492899,
      "updated": 1781492907
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ca60000000000882efc",
      "text": "\t\tここはほとんど使ってなくて、キーボードショーカットの入力が必要な時だけに使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492903,
      "updated": 1781492929
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6ca10000000000882efa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492897,
      "updated": 1781492897
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6af30000000000882ee6",
      "text": "\t[[https://gyazo.com/1a316820e719aced58e502d40995d9c3]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492468,
      "updated": 1781492489
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6c980000000000882ef7",
      "text": "\t\t4番レイヤー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492888,
      "updated": 1781492935
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6cc70000000000882efd",
      "text": "\t\tこれも3番レイヤーと同じくキーボードショートカットを入力する時のみ使ってます",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492935,
      "updated": 1781492954
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2f6b140000000000882ee8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781492500,
      "updated": 1781492500
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bb525000000000089c119",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783346469,
      "updated": 1783346469
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bb513000000000089c118",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon][nyarla]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783346452,
      "updated": 1783346464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bafce000000000089c0cb",
      "text": "#自作キーボード",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783345102,
      "updated": 1783345114
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bafd5000000000089c0cc",
      "text": "#使っているキーボード",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783345110,
      "updated": 1783345123
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4bafe5000000000089c0ce",
      "text": "#キーボードの配列",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783345125,
      "updated": 1783345134
    }
  ]
}